This is exactly why philosophers like:
	•	Nick Bostrom
	•	Stuart Russell
	•	Daniel Dennett

talk about alignment not just as a machine problem but a human values problem.

Because before aligning AI…

We have to figure out:

Aligned with what?

Human morality itself is still evolving.

